name: 6th International Conference on Bioscience & Engineering
content: 6th International Conference on Bioscience & Engineering (BIEN 2023) will provide an excellent International forum for sharing knowledge and results in theory, methodology and applications impacts and challenges of Bioscience and Engineering. The goal of this Conference is to bring together researchers and practitioners from academia and industry to focus on Bioscience and Engineering advancements and establishing new collaborations in these areas. Original research papers, state-of-the-art reviews are invited for publication in all areas of Bioscience and Engineering.
